## In caso si rompe tutto: 
    1) Downgrade del kernel: 
        cd /var/cache/pacman/pkg
        pacman -U linux-4.xx.xx
    2) Inserisci live cd/chiavetta:
        mount /dev/sdaX /mnt
        mount /dev/sdaY /mnt/boot
        arch-chroot /mnt /bin/bash
        mkinitcpio -p linux


